title: THE JACK BENNY PROGRAM -- Billy Graham ( 14th Season Premiere )
description:
This 1963 season opener ( the last on CBS ) was shot on videotape and transferred to film. 

By the mid 1950s Jack's shows were usually filmed to begin with, 
but this orginated from CBS Television City in Hollywood -- where they had 
done live shows back in the early seasons, as those alternated with 
filmed episodes beginning with Season 4.
